From: hmaarrfk <mark.harfouche@conda-forge.org>
Date: 2026-05-10
Subject: umd: gate unit_tests subdirs on a new ENABLE_NPU_UNIT_TESTS flag

The umd CMakeLists.txt unconditionally `add_subdirectory()`s
vpu_driver/unit_tests and level_zero_driver/unit_tests. Both pull in
GoogleTest/GoogleMock headers and only exist for developer-style unit
tests of the userspace driver. Downstream packagers that ship the
runtime driver have no use for them, and forcing them to either vendor
GoogleTest or carry a googletest find_package wrapper just to shut these
subdirs up is unnecessary churn.

Introduce a separate option ENABLE_NPU_UNIT_TESTS (default OFF) that
gates both unit_tests subdir adds. The validation/ tree, which has its
own larger test app and is gated by ENABLE_VALIDATION_BUILD, is
untouched.

Paths in this patch are prefixed with `linux-npu-driver-1.32.1/`
because conda-build extracts this source with `no_hoist: true` and
applies patches from the recipe's work_dir (one level above the
upstream root).
---
 linux-npu-driver-1.32.1/CMakeLists.txt     | 1 +
 linux-npu-driver-1.32.1/umd/CMakeLists.txt | 8 ++++++--
 2 files changed, 7 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)
diff --git a/linux-npu-driver-1.32.1/CMakeLists.txt b/linux-npu-driver-1.32.1/CMakeLists.txt
index ffff02f..d682665 100644
--- a/linux-npu-driver-1.32.1/CMakeLists.txt
+++ b/linux-npu-driver-1.32.1/CMakeLists.txt
@@ -43,6 +43,7 @@ option(ENABLE_COMPILATION_FLAGS_OVERRIDE "Allow to override flags passed to comp
 # The npu_elf target is picked up from the compiler package
 option(ENABLE_NPU_ELF_BUILD "Enable building NPU Elf library in driver" OFF)
 option(ENABLE_TOOLS_BUILD "Enable building tools" OFF)
+option(ENABLE_NPU_UNIT_TESTS "Enable building umd unit tests (requires GoogleTest)" OFF)
 
 message(STATUS "option ENABLE_NPU_COMPILER_BUILD: ${ENABLE_NPU_COMPILER_BUILD}")
 message(STATUS "option ENABLE_NPU_PERFETTO_BUILD: ${ENABLE_NPU_PERFETTO_BUILD}")
diff --git a/linux-npu-driver-1.32.1/umd/CMakeLists.txt b/linux-npu-driver-1.32.1/umd/CMakeLists.txt
index 680a874..d6b3527 100644
--- a/linux-npu-driver-1.32.1/umd/CMakeLists.txt
+++ b/linux-npu-driver-1.32.1/umd/CMakeLists.txt
@@ -59,8 +59,12 @@ include_directories(${VPU_SOURCE_DIR})
 include_directories(SYSTEM ${VPU_KMD_INCLUDE_DIR})
 
 add_subdirectory_unique(vpu_driver/source)
-add_subdirectory_unique(vpu_driver/unit_tests)
+if (ENABLE_NPU_UNIT_TESTS)
+    add_subdirectory_unique(vpu_driver/unit_tests)
+endif()
 
 add_subdirectory_unique(level_zero_driver/source)
-add_subdirectory_unique(level_zero_driver/unit_tests)
+if (ENABLE_NPU_UNIT_TESTS)
+    add_subdirectory_unique(level_zero_driver/unit_tests)
+endif()
 add_subdirectory_unique(level_zero_driver/api)
